					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->DEAR MAYO CLINIC:&nbsp;My husband has been diagnosed with cancer. I know his treatment will be hard on him, and I want to help in any way with his diet. What do you recommend for us? ANSWER:&nbsp;Cancer treatments can take a toll on a person's body. Your husband's treatment may cause nausea, changes in appetite, taste […]<p></p>
