					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->DEAR MAYO CLINIC:&nbsp;Our neighbors were selling their home and had it tested for radon. The test was positive. Why should we be concerned about radon, and should we have our home tested too? ANSWER:&nbsp;The positive test for radon in your neighbors' home has given you a heads-up that your home should be tested as well. […]<p></p>
