		<title>New CT imaging oral contrast agent improves visualization of bowel anatomy, clinical trial data show</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/new-ct-imaging-oral-contrast-agent-improves-visualization-of-bowel-anatomy-clinical-trial-data-show/
		
